                "date": "2026-07-08T12:33:19Z"
            },
            "message": "[test] Fix Error Proxy stack assignment in Node.js 21+ (#36967)\n\nSame as #35227, but for `set`.\n\nV8's `stack` setter silently noops when `this` is a Proxy\n(nodejs/node#60862), so prodstack-stripping assignments like\n`error.stack = 'Error: ' + message` in `resolveErrorProd` were dropped\nand reads returned the real stack.\n\nThis caused `yarn test --prod` failures on Node 21+.\n\n## Test Plan\n\n`yarn test --prod` passes on both old and new Nodes.\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
            "tree": {
                "sha": "69b3ecbd663331076a120d5630680fffb6d9cd04",
                "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/react/react/git/trees/69b3ecbd663331076a120d5630680fffb6d9cd04"
            },
            "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/react/react/git/commits/e3e813d4d6cd61746676f207f0847c744fb3ad64",
            "comment_count": 0,
            "verification": {
                "verified": true,
                "reason": "valid",
                "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\nwsFcBAABCAAQBQJqTkOPCRC1aQ7uu5UhlAAAybwQABOi3fzHeXlNm6H6CQfcmjRT\naRdyjJhh/LUST1XAmQuylQEZbbrOPgtp6L4ftyh6gnOhau2Ioex1m9DnGAOjIfmk\n5yvo6HBwXS3A4ihnLt5J6FzomuQaqplDQaO++HtdGaqnBIOe2lLMyDJ4/Gd786CO\nkYsO3wmvO04vsA++uK6S+Twex6bTf0v9HHMhJFf3e1Cweme5AVTEGhtK7IxA8zWd\ngADpDnQvsbhzNckVKuzEiEwXCICknIAXRzKmtKkNd/7JYsU6PNQGfTsTR9zXWUc/\nnqlWxHD727kx875YGlaIa/oiV/yaL+5Xw8ASumQCBxsQ5uam4fnXv8qonHGRK1sK\nZM4wamLSzBm4T/GYCp/Z5B86XijvM8W8chQbzLZzTHw8ijmIs9YwS6Dc8xW3krwW\n4GtP4je/W2e1hpWns/XeNVOGs2o3DzJ8a4mpMMjxaADi/VYQsJbf/RcMJIyOR6Av\n8Fj0myiM6++TTdZrTSaKlZ2yMhgSq9zoGj642pGyOa0fayFiVB/4jWk7vVUt5mJk\nCRF50XSYKA196quf5ReFCXjOSrNI8Drv7tgB1JjfmhH8czdj4J2ZKgri1nJQ4dzH\nQpSP2RoH8x9M8CjoinaFXjNS66x9XKZB1ogs89mawdBll/av5B3HruRKQ7EnXQvz\nlBOnBlcUfqRlghvt0Ksw\n=DTFP\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----\n",
                "payload": "tree 69b3ecbd663331076a120d5630680fffb6d9cd04\nparent 994ebf9dce1708045d9570f2fab7702be4763f97\nauthor dan <dan.abramov@me.com> 1783513999 +0100\ncommitter GitHub <noreply@github.com> 1783513999 +0100\n\n[test] Fix Error Proxy stack assignment in Node.js 21+ (#36967)\n\nSame as #35227, but for `set`.\n\nV8's `stack` setter silently noops when `this` is a Proxy\n(nodejs/node#60862), so prodstack-stripping assignments like\n`error.stack = 'Error: ' + message` in `resolveErrorProd` were dropped\nand reads returned the real stack.\n\nThis caused `yarn test --prod` failures on Node 21+.\n\n## Test Plan\n\n`yarn test --prod` passes on both old and new Nodes.\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
